ckModal_main_3616372\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104upz1665702636480.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/upz1665702636480.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/upz1665702636480.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"upz1665702636480\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify whether the header should be displayed at the top of the List View:\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"upz1665702636480__p_d107114e1_d107115e1_d107116e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>Header<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> |\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"upz1665702636480__table_d12632e1_d12633e1_d12634e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"upz1665702636480__table_d12632e1_d12633e1_d12634e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"upz1665702636480__table_d12632e1_d12633e1_d12634e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upz1665702636480__table_d12632e1_d12633e1_d12634e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upz1665702636480__table_d12632e1_d12633e1_d12634e1__entry__2\">The list view is displayed with header.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upz1665702636480__table_d12632e1_d12633e1_d12634e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upz1665702636480__table_d12632e1_d12633e1_d12634e1__entry__2\">The list view is displayed without header. In\n                     effect, this disables dynamic sorting of the list items.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"upz1665702636480__section_ls3_dqk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1157446e112\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"upz1665702636480__table_d12635e1_d12636e1_d12637e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported in Grid?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Disabled if the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">List\n                           View</span> is not <code class=\"ph codeph\">R</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"upz1665702636480__section_fnn_2qk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1157446e167\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"upz1665702636480__p_d107123e1_d107124e1_d107125e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zie1665702558978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of a field.\">$properties</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1705998763272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.\">$fieldproperties</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"upz1665702636480__pre_yjx_fqk_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"header=false\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"upz1665702636480__section_gvc_gqk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1157446e199\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gge1665702634237.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" title=\"The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.\">utree (Tree)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qlx1665702636554.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>List View Style (ListView)</a><p>Format of data is displayed in the List View.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616372\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616372\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Show Header ( Header) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify whether the header should be displayed at the top of the List View: \" Header = True | False \" Value Description True The list view is displayed with header. False The list view is displayed without header. In effect, this disables dynamic sorting of the list items. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Disabled if the List View is not R . Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see $properties and $fieldproperties . $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"header=false\" Copy Applies To utree (Tree) Related Links List View Style (ListView) Format of data is displayed in the List View. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}